\id HAG  
\h Haggai 
\mt1 Haggai  
\toc1 Haggai 
\toc2 Haggai  
\c 1  
\s1 Haggai.  
\sr Haggai 1.8  
\p
\v 8 Yamba nyubun bama burri Haggai, nyulu kuku Godundumun manin, balkan Israel-warranda. Nyulu yalaman, “Dungayda manjalba, timber mana, Godumu bayan kunbay-mana.” Jana Israel-warra dungan, Godumu bayan ngarankuda.   